::DevilDuer/Bloodystrike/Reptilica::

Running down a hallway at full speed, DevilDuer glances at his 
scanners, nearly crashing into a wall as he sees that the femm had 
taken a route toward the bridge.

"All blast doors in section two, CLOSE!" he yells at the nearest 
console he comes to, blast doors slamming down hallways around the 
area with the bridge, about 10 feet apart from each other. The doors
, 
however, didn't block out the ventalation system, although it was 
still sealed from the outside world.

His gun ready, DevilDuer sets off down a hallway.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Expecting the door of the Alliance base to open and let him in, 
Reptilica flies up to it without slowing down, crashing and falling
to 
the ground, unconscious. Bloodystrike lands near him.

"What in the pit's goin' on?!" he asks the base, frowning when the 
computer reports that there's an intruder in the base and that no one 
is to enter or exit untill the situation is taken care of.

Bloodystrike sighs, picking up Reptilica and walking off toward the 
shuttle that Reptilica had brought the three Vok in.
